---
import { investmentIncludes, site } from "../config/site";
---
<section
  class="py-section-gap-mobile md:py-section-gap-desktop bg-pit-lane-navy border-y border-white/5 reveal-hidden"
  id="investimento"
>
  <div class="px-gutter max-w-container-max mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 md:mb-14 reveal-hidden">
      <p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-primary tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Transparência</p>
      <h2 class="font-section-title text-section-title text-performance-white uppercase">
        Investimento: <span class="text-primary">{site.investment}</span>
        <span class="block text-performance-white text-[0.55em] mt-2 tracking-[0.08em]">por participante</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-metallic-grey mt-6 max-w-[65ch]">
        O valor funciona como marcador de entrada para um dia inteiro de experiência, pilotagem e conexões de alto nível em Interlagos.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-start">
      <ul class="lg:col-span-7 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-5">
        {investmentIncludes.map((item) => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-[20px] mt-0.5 shrink-0">check_circle</span>
            <span class="font-body-md text-body-md text-performance-white/90 leading-relaxed">{item}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5 bg-track-asphalt/80 border border-white/10 p-8 md:p-10">
        <p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-primary tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Como funciona</p>
        <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-metallic-grey mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Esta página não finaliza a compra. Você solicita participação, nossa equipe qualifica seu perfil e orienta sobre os próximos passos de pagamento.
        </p>
        <a
          class="inline-flex w-full justify-center items-center bg-podium-gold text-on-primary font-label-caps text-label-caps px-8 py-4 uppercase tracking-widest transition-all duration-300 btn-glow hover:opacity-90"
          href="#aplicacao"
        >
          SOLICITAR MINHA PARTICIPAÇÃO
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
